msg: Start building the component rendering framework for the grid.
This breaks the pager rendering code out of the PagerModel and into an IPagerRenderer interface with an AbstractPagerRenderer implementation.  The two current pager models extend this interface.
Fixup dependent classes to use these implementations and remove pagerStyle support from the PagerModel.
Also disable the SortService and FilterService for the time being.
